WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Colorit' is a Workbench game in which there are two square
boards filled with coloured tiles. The board at left has a pattern
and the other is randomly shuffled. The goal of the game is to
move the tiles of the shuffled board in order to match the other
board in the least amount of moves possible.

  You play by clicking on a tile, which must be surrounded by 8
tiles. Each time you click on a tile, the game will 'rotate' the
surrounding tiles clockwise by one position.

  Have fun!

